<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Register</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/auth.css">
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Register</h1>
  <p>Please fill in the form below to create your account. Your username must be unique, and your password should be at least 8 characters long. For better security, we recommend using a combination of uppercase and lowercase letters, numbers, and special characters.</p>
  <form action="/register" method="POST">
    <input type="text" name="username" placeholder="Username" required />
    <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="Password" required />
    <button type="submit">Register</button>
  </form>
  <p>Already have an account? <a href="/login">Login here</a>.</p>
</body>
</html>
